short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension monitors browser activity and websites accessed.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A companion extension for ByteMonk inTact product. This extension enforces corporate policies regarding internet websites. Extension will not work without ByteMonk inTact installed on the native system.
